Welcome to Speech Telepathy.

This game relies on voice commands, as well as the arrow keys.

Try clicking the   button and saying the word "left".

Commands:


"Left" Moves left

"Right" Moves Right

"Up" Moves Up

"Diagonal Left" Moves Up and Left

"Diagonal Right" Moves Up and Right


Click Anywhere to Resume
